snippet.title: PDX Guitar Freak
snippet.description:
I got my first guitar at the age of 12, in 1983, with dreams of being the next Eddie Van Halen. Like many other aspiring young musicians, the reality of having to get a real job and eventually support a family, made me move down with a different path. Along came the advent of YouTube and the ability to share my passion with others through this medium, which rekindled my playing in a way that I never anticipated. I appreciate you all for watching, and for the inspiration you continue to give me every day. :)

In addition to guitar lessons, I'm also open to reviewing gear and doing demos. If you have a product you want me to review or promote, drop me a line.
